{"tid":448535,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"今年 AOS 不設退貨","createTime":"2017-10-26T10:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T09:22:24.000Z","uid":64181,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0150dee57453959e50b5e571bb9fcfe489e6951b","tid":448535,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:03:41.000Z","msg":"相信經歷了 iPhone 8 的預習後，大家已知今年的 AOS 不設退貨。Apple 退貨及更換政策列出，「所有於香港 Apple Store 購買的產品均不設退貨及更換。我們僅對有瑕疵的產品作出特殊的更換處理。」<br />\n<br />\n另一點要留意的是，3 次送貨不成的物品，也會視為取消訂單，並收取 15% 的退貨費用。Apple 退貨及更換政策列明，「如果 3 次送貨仍未能成功，我們會向你發送一封電郵，要求你於 3 天內聯絡我們安排再次送貨。如果我們在 3 天內未能收到回覆，或再次送貨仍未能成功，我們會將訂單產品視作取消，並向你收取 15% 的退貨費用。」因此，大家如將 iPhone 當作炒賣用途，記緊衡量風險。"},{"pid":"fd09185e992e64784e92ff23d785cefea1115e20","tid":448535,"uid":64181,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2017/09/23/261926/wnnp002p02a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2017%2F09%2F23%2F261926%2Fwnnp002p02a.jpg&h=b22ca6e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07e34242368bacee518d3c475c4bde9ac3002283","tid":448535,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T13:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0253e9bcacffff307a71dfcc42da476451142a1","tid":448535,"uid":64181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T15:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bbd7157c520e9ee1f22d2d70cbffeddf7c6ae20","tid":448535,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T15:17:14.000Z","msg":"炒家必死<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj